# Personal AI conversation data — never commit, keep the repo safe to open-source.
# Live chat stores live under state/ (below) and solo_rag_chat/_solo_data, but these
# explicit patterns are defense-in-depth in case a store is relocated or a raw export
# is dropped into the tree for ingestion.
**/_solo_data/
**/notes/chats/
**/notes/spaces/
**/chats/chat_*.json
# Transferred-knowledge memory built from ingested AI chat exports (transcripts,
# summaries, detected memory files, the provenance ledger) plus its FAISS index.
**/notes/ingested_memory/
**/notes/ingested_memory_rag_index/
# RAG vector indexes built from personal notes/chats.
**/notes/notes_rag_index/
**/rag_index/
# AI provider keys (plaintext API keys live here).
**/ai_settings.json
# Raw exported chat histories (Claude / ChatGPT "Export data") dropped in for import.
**/conversations.json
**/projects.json
**/users.json

# Local app state, databases, and WAL/SHM sidecars.
state/
gallery/*.db
gallery/*.db-*
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

